{"tid":2275170,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［勸世文］真係唔好去觀塘間韓家買外賣","createTime":"2020-11-07T03:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T18:46:52.000Z","uid":249557,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"367424f7613e522172b8cffe60df9a1e5798d566","tid":2275170,"uid":249557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"事緣琴日lunch時間去觀塘間韓家叫咗五個炸雞便當（1:36）<br />\n同場有另一Team嘅同事（隔離Team入去堂食我哋外賣自取）<br />\n<br />\n然後一直喺門口等見到差唔多時間買便當既人都有得拎<br />\n已經覺得唔對路 即刻入去問個女店員（2:05）<br />\n但係佢冇解釋係咁話準備緊<br />\n過到5分鐘都仲係未有就再問多次啦<br />\n就突然有另一個解釋話今日個廚房唔知做乜嘢<br />\n心諗唔知咩解釋黎 人地堂食個d餐又冇事<br />\n隔離team同事已經食完啦<br />\n你堂食外賣分開兩個廚房阿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到我哋拎到外賣嗰陣已經係2:15<br />\n即刻狗衝返Office 10分鐘啪飯盒<br />\n<br />\n事後聽返堂食同事講話聽到個男員工講<br />\n梗係做晒d堂食先啦 貴價餐嚟㗎嘛 （意譯）<br />\n仲問個女店員點解咁蠢走出去俾人屌<br />\n<br />\n大佬雖然我知黃店係有光環<br />\n但你係黃店之前 首先係一間餐廳<br />\n要做返一間餐廳應該有既服務質素<br />\n但你宜家當正d外賣客人乞衣咁<br />\n幾黃都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日上佢哋Facebook睇到佢哋之前出咗個post<br />\n但係講嘅嘢完全同佢做嘢根本係背道而馳<br />\n奉勸各位如果唔係有無限lunch時間嘅就唔好去嗰度買外賣啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3nAkex.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3nAkex.png&h=5a99a0e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e3b58a87aa36ccfb9a8f9c8fab7ee20fab15b00","tid":2275170,"uid":37197,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:06:03.000Z","msg":"今日個廚房唔知做乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOn9回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc4ebf46d3961ad283c82fa5b6b73ac929a05d8","tid":2275170,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e536f1028a199741efa277091eeeccdecb1b5d","tid":2275170,"uid":169819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"我半年前叫過一次外賣 又係等左成半粒鐘 但堂食果d嚟得好快 之後就冇再食過..."},{"pid":"3df4597e2eb802291d7908e7c7e9f82bcd22c007","tid":2275170,"uid":126372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872c59de4bbc4fb0ca85cf59c689065104a2ac5f","tid":2275170,"uid":70439,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:39:45.000Z","msg":"幫襯呢啲黃店真係貼錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea000f97b7f0cb140237c3cc758162bc4eee443","tid":2275170,"uid":104865,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"叫佢改善下la咁好過直接叫人唔去 話曬黃店"},{"pid":"043fd26ed1eaa67218448a6823e074f278f64c98","tid":2275170,"uid":254191,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"堂食dinner食過 好難食"},{"pid":"31a8a63a8bd9aafdd84b03f0f75cb458648305a4","tid":2275170,"uid":312429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:20:12.000Z","msg":"堂食過佢哋炸雞放題 漏單出餐慢之餘仲要唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ceae030759fe4cea1b86794a1a4c36be220cf4","tid":2275170,"uid":9069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T11:13:12.000Z","msg":"不嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搭三去等到搭九<br />\n不過幾好味"},{"pid":"e09aa7341e8d9137f15410b09cd0bf9bccf1bc47","tid":2275170,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"佢啲醬好似油漆/新鮮嘅血"},{"pid":"e9f0