改善咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43840a3040ad1eb2d7c56c6b0e10d469c164d3e4","tid":2275170,"uid":376837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"338284082d6af5a0d9ba515c542fbe4196f4800e","tid":2275170,"uid":34147,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"大半年前執食過炸雞放題，雖然出餐慢咗少少，但應該係我喺香港食過頭三名好食嘅炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞肉夠滑、又juicy （估計係生炸），最撚緊要係個蜜糖醬較到啱啱好，唔會太膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但就真係等得好q 耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa861bebb3107ec76f787546ef836224f671447a","tid":2275170,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"近期堂食過芝士炸雞拉麵 等候時間同味道都正常"},{"pid":"398f90a1b2e32e173add0e78698367a50cfc8067","tid":2275170,"uid":364900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"年頭個時食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD雞係幾好食既<br />\n其他野就一般<br />\n但堂食仲等得耐過外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專做外賣算啦"},{"pid":"f8d888e007c274ea3c9ef9f4868a417d134bdc6e","tid":2275170,"uid":249557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398f90a1b2e32e173add0e78698367a50cfc8067","tid":2275170,"uid":364900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"年頭個時食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD雞係幾好食既<br />\n其他野就一般<br />\n但堂食仲等得耐過外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專做外賣算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"堂食等得耐過外賣真係有d匪夷所思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你堂食平價餐?"},{"pid":"ba0cc44273fb88e1731967cb17380fbf77eca111","tid":2275170,"uid":78707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"屌叫過幾次外賣自取<br />\n有次叫左個咩醬油香蒜味炸雞<br />\n滿心期待咁番到屋企先發現佢無比個汁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個刻成日既心情即刻跌到落谷底<br />\n不過等好耐係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1060d191ac5fe3e9aa898a43c079c0ecce3a5db2","tid":2275170,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"人血炸雞"}]}